    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1183357900">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1183357900" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1183357900" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1183357900">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49257924/">YypJs</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">乱。且作者语言文字水平不高。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
